PresenceUserConfigProfile.name: PresenceUserConfigProfile
PresenceUserConfigProfile.description: Represents a configuration that determines the settings that are assigned to presence users who are assigned to a specific profile. User-level configurations override profile-level configurations.

PresenceUserConfigId.description: If an individual user is also assigned a presence configuration through the PresenceUserConfigProfile, this configuration will override that.

ProfileId.description: The ID of the profile thatâ€™s associated with this presence configuration. A profile can be associated with only one presence configuration.
